high_descs: Head to the dresser on the left.
Pick up the keys from the dresser.
Turn left to exit the room and turn right to walk to the end of the passage to reach the lamp.
Switch on the green lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the keys under the lamp light.

high_descs: Turn to your left, move straight to the table
Pick up the key on the table
Turn to your left, walk straight, turn to your right, go straight, again turn to your right, walk straight to the end to the big lamp in the corner
Turn on the big lamp in the corner
anns.task_desc: Examine the key by the big lamp in the corner

high_descs: Turn around and walt to the cabinet to your left.
PIck up the keys that are on your right.
Turn around to the wall to your left, turn right to the exit. When you reach the corridor, cross to the right. Reach the lamp and turn it on.
Do not move.
anns.task_desc: Take the keys and bring them to where the lamp is and turn it on.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the dresser.
Take the keychain from the table.
Turn around and go near the floorlamp.
Put the keys near the floorlamp it will be glow.
anns.task_desc: To glow the FloorLamp using the KeyChain.

high_descs: Go near to the dresser.
Pick the keychain from the table.
Exit the room and turn right go straight to reach the floorlamp.
Turn on the floorlamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine KeyChain by the light of a tall FloorLamp.

high_descs: watching to the room
Take the keychain to the table.
near by to the floorlamp
Turn on the floorlamp using the key.
anns.task_desc: Use the KeyChain to turn on the FloorLamp.
